  Note.  Estimates in this table are based on the North American Industry 
     Classification System (NAICS).Chained (1996) dollar series for real 
     change in private inventories are calculated as the period-to-period 
     change in chained-dollar end-of-period inventories.Quarterly changes 
     in end-of-period inventories are stated at annual rates.Because the 
     formula for the chain-type quantity indexes uses weights of more than 
     one period, the corresponding chained-dollar estimates are usually not 
     additive.
